 help every boarding school from all around the world, provide exceptional care for their boarding students. But while growth as a business is important, our team and values are just as paramount. <br/><br/>Instead of chasing overnight success, our team is committed to producing a quality product and service that is built to go the distance.<br/><br/>That&#x27;s why we prioritise our energy to your biggest challenges and pains in boarding. We strive to listen and truly understand your problems, then carefully design and implement features with quality infrastructure that will have the greatest impact on your lives for many years to come.</p></div><h2 class="h2-center">Meet our team</h2><div class="collection-wrapper-team w-dyn-list"><div class="w-dyn-items w-row"><div class="collection-item-team w-dyn-item w-col w-col-4"><div class="collection-team-div"><div class="w-row"><div class="collection-team-col centre w-col w-col-4 w-col-small-4 w-col-tiny-4"><div class="team-profile-div"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/5b219b78a710aa89f7fe9cc9/5b2843ce3dd6e1fefa23e9b9_P1070348.jpg" alt="" class="collection-team-profile-image"/></div></div><div class="collection-team-col w-col w-col-8 w-col-small-8 w-col-tiny-8"><div class="profile-info-div"><div class="collection-team-text-name">Paul Organ</div><div class="collection-team-text-title">Co-founder &amp; Co-CEO</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collection-item-team w-dyn-item w-col w-col-4"><div class="collection-team-div"><div class="w-row"><div class="collection-team-col centre w-col w-col-4 w-col-small-4 w-col-tiny-4"><div class="team-profile-div"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/5b219b78a710aa89f7fe9cc9/5b2825ac3c33f01105fd4271_Kurt.png" alt="" class="collection-team-profile-image"/></div></div><div class="collection-team-col w-col w-col-8 w-col-small-8 w-col-tiny-8"><div class="profile-info-div"><div class="collection-team-text-name">Kurt Meyer</div><div class="collection-team-text-title">C